    <h1 class="c-page-title">An Exhaustive Ranking of Movie Journalists</h1>

    <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">From ‘His Girl Friday’ to ‘A Beautiful Day in the Neighborhood,’ which movie muckrakers get their stories, break the most news, and, most importantly, avoid sleeping with their subjects?</p>

