px), 100vw" alt="" data-upload-width="1481" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nvWHs7mT1vlRwg68_0DnVnLstv4=/0x0:1481x1000/1200x0/filters:focal(0x0:1481x1000):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394321/barrymore_never_been_kissed.jpg">

