  <source srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/kg0VeaZfF36BJCaOSKiHccXKDD0=/0x0:1777x918/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VWEz1jlOnEmWiJ60Vi4l1h_AhuQ=/0x0:1777x918/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/17Lf_sg7h_1ZuanDdO-X1SA3COE=/0x0:1777x918/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/uVZnHnGSr8VvaQAVeDOJ_b3osx8=/0x0:1777x918/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/E93SlxPDbxSCF38t_tn0sgeG3jQ=/0x0:1777x918/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/n9M3bXfGOs2BygRpJEhEu9ZHgH4=/0x0:1777x918/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/I4Tr3lqICs-6kRam0TeLVCu1LEo=/0x0:1777x918/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/u3KFMoLmFbKeRTy5oRWnx4979VA=/0x0:1777x918/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gCK4EXUhQEOi1Fh0YwsXZq6TmC0=/0x0:1777x918/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" type="image/webp">


<img srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/v0HrIegddHHwfPejZsBDFnYS-M8=/0x0:1777x918/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/mGhcGOZob4SllAJfnUhhcK5qISo=/0x0:1777x918/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yMbVyhqKrsfGw3us6GvJkkNz29c=/0x0:1777x918/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gqErw5kE-K3rYRD3W5iIUnzDe5I=/0x0:1777x918/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-eJrkQ8DpHD-4L4KwSVeoRSqzxk=/0x0:1777x918/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9Bi--13rErdSkPCwc2VhUVXWxM8=/0x0:1777x918/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R5-nS-yNoGMfvKeo7E-UelH75ak=/0x0:1777x918/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/C6STUpYEKIWDcSJluA_IOSxPK4A=/0x0:1777x918/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lXS3zj1CrKMzGSpAtpRteIXLO3U=/0x0:1777x918/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" alt="" data-upload-width="1777" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/vztQeQ1-N4ZDo9JUD_ptYvlNBHM=/0x0:1777x918/1200x0/filters:focal(0x0:1777x918):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394324/schumer_trainwreck.jpg">

</source></picture>

      
    </span>
    
  </span>
  
    <span class="e-image__meta">
      
      
        <cite>Universal Pictures</cite>
      
    </span>
  
</figure>

<p id="ibNGup">Schumer’s Townsend is a hard-partying men’s magazine writer who falls in love with the subject of her story, a handsome sports doctor. </p>
<p id="KL6i6l"><strong>Does the character get their story? </strong>Yes, somehow it is published in <em>Vanity Fair </em>after Townsend is fired from her original job for almost sleeping with its 16-year-old intern. <strong>10/10</strong> I guess? </p>
<p id="QNLU12"><strong>Are they competent? </strong>I repeat: Townsend is fired for almost sleeping with a 16-year-old intern.<strong> 0/10 </strong></p>
<p id="D2SsJO"><strong>Are they ethical?</strong> In addition to almost sleeping with said intern, Townsend sleeps with her story’s subject. <strong>minus-10/10 </strong></p>
<p id="FoYjwd"><strong>How believable is the journalist? </strong>I know a lot of journalists who live like Townsend—minus the sleeping with sources and nearly sleeping with 16-year-olds, thank God—so we’ll go with <strong>4/10</strong>. </p>
<p id="gyJpyn"><strong>Total: 4/40</strong></p>
<h4 id="LZtRoe">35. Meg Ryan as Annie Reed in<em> Sleepless in Seattle </em>(1993) </h4>
<p id="iflRMa">Reed is a <em>Baltimore Sun </em>reporter who becomes obsessed with a Seattle-based widower (Tom Hanks) even though she is engaged to Walter (Bill Pullman), a kind man she actually knows. </p>
<p id="kJ5Rpl"><strong>Does the character get their story? </strong>Even though Reed flies to Seattle to write about Sad Tom Hanks for the<em> Sun</em>, she never actually files anything about him. <strong>0/10</strong></p>
<p id="3iuECe"><strong>Are they competent? </strong>Reed is good at navigating the internet for a person from the 1990s and is able to track down the identities of Sad Tom Hanks and his son shockingly quickly, so she does get <strong>1/10</strong> for investigation skills, but no other points because she clearly can’t hit deadlines. </p>
<p id="ntbsxr"><strong>Are they ethical?</strong> She hires a private investigator to trail the subjects of a personal interest story, which seems like overkill and also something you need to get permission from editors to do? She also thinks her story subject is her soulmate. So I suppose it’s best she never filed.<strong> minus-5/10 </strong></p>
<p id="9N3cjt"><strong>How believable is the journalist? </strong>Reed is a neurotic stress case who loves to snoop and make bad choices. Yes. <strong>9/10 </strong></p>
<p id="ME4Rpa"><strong>Total 5/40</strong></p>
<h4 id="abHWt3">34. Johnny Depp as Raoul Duke in <em>Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas </em>(1998) </h4>
  <figure class="e-image">
  <span class="e-image__inner">
    
    <span class="e-image__image " data-original="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394329/depp_fear_and_loathing.jpg">
      
