<p id="LVaG2L"><strong>How believable is the journalist? </strong>Again, journalists don’t sleep with their subjects—I don’t know what we need to do to get screenwriters to realize this. But the opening scene when he stops his news helicopter to flirt feels all too real, and if a journalist were to sleep with a story subject ... it would be this guy. <strong>5/10</strong></p>
<p id="n6RPrm"><strong>Total: 14/40 </strong></p>
<h4 id="P0KnuJ">31. William Alland as Jerry Thompson in <em>Citizen Kane </em>(1941) </h4>
<p id="PBYenJ">After newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane (Orson Welles) dies, Thompson goes looking for the meaning of his final word, “Rosebud.” </p>
<p id="3K7Wz5"><strong>Does the character get their story? </strong>Nope. Thompson never figures it out. Considering Kane never told anyone about Rosebud, it’s not really Thompson’s fault, but the dude still completely whiffs on the assignment.<strong> 0/10 </strong></p>
<p id="fP8nQ7"><strong>Are they competent? </strong>He does a lot of good reporting about Kane’s life, and, had he been tasked with a less-granular assignment, he likely would have succeeded, so:<strong> 5/10</strong>.</p>
<p id="tYy67O"><strong>Are they ethical?</strong> He doesn’t go around breaking any major rules, but he also doesn’t really do much at all, so let’s settle in the middle: <strong>5/10</strong> </p>
<p id="NIPu8K"><strong>How believable is the journalist? </strong>Thompson is so very much a framing device in this movie that you don’t even really get to see his face; he’s a terrific bridge between flashbacks, but too nondescript to be believable or not.<strong> 5/10 </strong></p>
<p id="6Ez15x"><strong>Total: 15/40 </strong></p>
<h4 id="bjQBNN">30. Will Ferrell as Ron Burgundy and Christina Applegate as Veronica Corningstone in<em> Anchorman: The Legend of Ron Burgundy </em>(2004) </h4>
  <figure class="e-image">
  <span class="e-image__inner">
    
    <span class="e-image__image " data-original="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg">
      
        <picture class="c-picture" data-cid="site/picture_element-1587430032_6_58881" data-cdata='{"asset_id":19394330,"ratio":"*"}'>
  


  <source srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/e46jc1nmxGlbBlXcaWVfR3pX2RY=/0x0:1500x999/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/16Lsf15hWR7qEnX-j0vdzw0aMhA=/0x0:1500x999/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NehXVAuEKz6RVhLrHrVMLLgdBSc=/0x0:1500x999/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Yv4gdX9U5ayOkd3rUh7nX1cXRZU=/0x0:1500x999/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4bOKWVR8lx-q1yPnp8nbGkTjE2A=/0x0:1500x999/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TR1cdjaDca51BzjAGtNFgpLI4HQ=/0x0:1500x999/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tLKnVp365yYhCNxPNltbZBg2Hos=/0x0:1500x999/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/92hBrjiZb-X-yEzUfdJ_KGgObpg=/0x0:1500x999/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/puSlc5ELBdIJRqCmOtEGYHWfFYM=/0x0:1500x999/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" type="image/webp">


<img srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/QPxAFpparQA_-6epKcMYmf0GdwQ=/0x0:1500x999/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gC2tH6RY8atnwulTHeTuRaT04LQ=/0x0:1500x999/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Mrzb6Ef_lYO1Q6TQd2k1uTRduGY=/0x0:1500x999/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wOZrghK2LvSMR9FqSzyiA8JP2e8=/0x0:1500x999/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bBsyElr02fAr5wWSYd-o0FFrznA=/0x0:1500x999/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lOLDafA-TSZuSrG91bae743eF1g=/0x0:1500x999/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IC1t8VjySbz7i3BioVFq7Eb3d3s=/0x0:1500x999/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6_feZA__qeMBHvY1aBhmS70_QT4=/0x0:1500x999/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7gWjrLH6ArzNottmvshmoeE4nac=/0x0:1500x999/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19394330/anchorman.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" alt="" data-upload-width="1500" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/e_1qV1_jtKGoKfrwD5G7gnWOSBA=/0x0:1500x999/1200x0/filters:focal(0x0:1500x999):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-c